  "openapi_surface": "OpenAPISpec() in openapi.go concatenates openAPISpecPrefix + eleven openapi_paths_*.go fragments + openAPIComponents, replacing __PCG_VERSION__ with buildinfo.AppVersion(). ServeOpenAPI serves this at GET /api/v0/openapi.json. ServeSwaggerUI serves a CDN-loaded Swagger UI at /api/v0/docs. ServeReDoc serves a CDN-loaded ReDoc at /api/v0/redoc.",
  "capability_matrix": "contract.go:127 defines capabilityMatrix, a map[string]capabilitySupport that gates truth level and required profile per capability. BuildTruthEnvelope(contract.go:383) consults this map and panics if a capability is missing. capabilityUnsupported(handler.go:105) returns true when maxTruthLevel returns nil for the current profile.",
